{"tid":1965782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★IT男確診未送院　任職光大新鴻基軟件開發組","createTime":"2020-04-09T16:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T05:27:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b386fa51298a2f888f0fb2dddbda295b35edabb","tid":1965782,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"有2人未能即日送院。其中一宗是銅鑼灣利園1期上班的43歲男子(第968宗個案)，屬於沒有外遊的源頭不明個案。據了解，患者為光大新鴻基資訊科技部軟件開發組員工，辦公室位於利園一期25樓全層，最後上班日期為上周五（3日）。利園一期所屬的希慎興業稱，已就相關樓層的共用空間及公共廁所消毒清潔。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心指患者上周六（4日）開始發燒，至本周三（8日）到瑪麗醫院求醫，9日確診。患者與家人居於上環文咸東街127號萬和閣，平日會在上環信德中心附近慢跑及在該區快餐店用膳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2615173/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%92IT%E7%94%B7%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%9C%AA%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E3%80%80%E4%BB%BB%E8%81%B7%E5%85%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E9%B4%BB%E5%9F%BA%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%B5%84%20-%E9%99%84%E5%B1%85%E6%89%80%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE-?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2615173%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%259C%2592IT%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E5%259F%25BA%25E8%25BB%259F%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%25B5%2584%2520-%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE-%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=b6b92908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2615173/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%92IT%E7%94%B7%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%9C%AA%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E3%80%80%E4%BB%BB%E8%81%B7%E5%85%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E9%B4%BB%E5%9F%BA%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%B5%84%20-%E9%99%84%E5%B1